text: Asanovo () is a rural locality (a selo) in Karmasansky Selsoviet, Ufimsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 427 as of 2010. There are 3 streets. == Geography == It is located 50 km from Ufa, 2 km from Karmasan. == References == Category:Rural localities in Ufimsky District
title: Asanovo, Republic of Bashkortostan
